    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1885-09-15T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1885-09-15T00:00:00-05:00" n="132" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d132">
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">No. 132.</seg>
                </opener>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Porter</persName> to Mr.
                                    <persName type="to">Cheng Tsao Ju</persName>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1885-09-15">
                            <hi rend="italic">September</hi> 15,
                                    1885</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Sir</hi>: I have had the honor to receive your note
                            of the 14th instant, concerning the departure on that date from San
                            Francisco of the members of the commission who are to investigate the
                            recent assault upon the Chinese laborers at Rock Springs, Wyoming
                            Territory, and stating that they expect to meet at Ogden City the
                            military escort appointed by the War Department to attend them. I have
                            had pleasure in communicating a copy of your note to the Secretary of
                            War.</p>
                <p>Accept, sir, &amp;c.,</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>JAS. D. PORTER,<lb/>
                        <hi rend="italic">Acting
                                Secretary.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
